y(d,"func:gasPointIssues");
s("dis","Gas Meter Point Issue");
s("ruleOn","equip and gas and meter");
s("param","(_,_,/*minTime:*/2hr,/*ruleWorkOrder:*/\"None\",/*priority:*/\"Medium\",/*type:*/\"Gas\")");
s("serviceCaseLevel","asset");
s("param2","(_,_,/*minTime:*/2hr,/*ruleWorkOrder:*/\"None\",/*priority:*/\"Medium\",/*type:*/\"Gas\")");
s("help","Gas meter points are reading value null or NA for more than 2hrs (adj).\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check power to the meters that are interfaced via high level integration (BACnet, modbus, etc). Also check for any faults in interface cards.\n2. Check power and network communication status of the controller to which the meter is connected.\n3. Check interface status if meter is communicating via high level integartion (BACnet, modbus, etc). Reset the communications between meter and controller/server to re-establish the connection.\n4. Check for damage in communication cable between meter and controller/server.\n5. For hardwired meters, check for any disconnected or broken wires, check meter and controller terminals for any damages or loose connections.");
s("name","gasPointIssues");
s("help2","Gas meter points are reading value null or NA for more than 2hrs (adj).\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check power to the meters that are interfaced via high level integration (BACnet, modbus, etc). Also check for any faults in interface cards.\n2. Check power and network communication status of the controller to which the meter is connected.\n3. Check interface status if meter is communicating via high level integartion (BACnet, modbus, etc). Reset the communications between meter and controller/server to re-establish the connection.\n4. Check for damage in communication cable between meter and controller/server.\n5. For hardwired meters, check for any disconnected or broken wires, check meter and controller terminals for any damages or loose connections.");
