s("help","Zone temp is higher than setpoint by 5°C (adj.) or more when cooling valve is fully open (>98%) & Heating valve is fully closed (<2%) and Fan status is On in occupied mode.\nThe above conditions were true for >60mins (2 times or more in a day) OR >120mins once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check if cooling valve is physically stuck.\n2. Check cooling valve actuator operation.\n3. Check if heating valve is passing.\n4. Check temp sensor location for any heat source.");
