s("help","Fan is running in Unoccupied periods when no Mode is calling for.\n\nThis Rule will trigger a Fault if:\n\nThe AHU Supply Fan is running (i.e. Fan Status is ON) when there are no Fan Enable/Start command from BMS. This rule checks Night Purge/Warm up/Night Setback modes, etc. too.\n\nThe above condition need to be true for minimum time period of 30min (adj.) to trigger the Fault.\n");
