s("param2","(_,_,/*minTime:*/30min,/*maxTime:*/60min,/*freq:*/2,/*ruleWorkOrder:*/\"None\",/*priority:*/\"High\",/*type:*/\"Energy\")");
s("help","Pump command and status both are On when associated Chillers/Boilers are Off.\nThe above conditions were true for >30mins (2 times or more in a day) OR >60mins once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check for pump command manual override on front end.\n2. Check pump software logic in controller.\n3. Check pump status sensor for any faults.");
