s("help","VAV Airflow sensor is higher than 1500 L/sec (adj) or lower than 10 L/sec (adj) when serving AHU status is ON.\n\nThe above conditions to remain true for >60mins (adj) 2 (adj) times or more in a day or >120mins (adj) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n  1. Check sensor for any faults/damage.\n  2. Check sensor to controller cable/wire faults, loose connections.\n  3. Verify voltage/current signals from sensor to controller terminals.\n     Verify power supply to sensor.\n  4. Check for any damage/faults in controller terminals.\n  5. Validate the sensor point characteristics in controller software.\n  6. Check manual overrides on front end/controller.");
