s("ruleOn","onCoil and temp and sensor");
s("param","(_,_,/*loLimit:*/5,/*hiLimit:*/60,/*minTime:*/30min,/*maxTime:*/60min,/*statuscheck:*/true,/*freq:*/2,/*ruleWorkOrder:*/\"None\",/*priority:*/\"Medium\",/*type:*/\"Operations\")");
s("param2","(_,_,/*loLimit:*/41,/*hiLimit:*/140,/*minTime:*/30min,/*maxTime:*/60min,/*statuscheck:*/true,/*freq:*/2,/*ruleWorkOrder:*/\"None\",/*priority:*/\"Medium\",/*type:*/\"Operations\")");
s("help","On Coil Supply temperature sensor is higher than 60°C (adj) or lower than 5°C (adj) when equipment status is On.\n\nThe above conditions to remain true for >30mins (adj) 2 (adj) times or more in a day or >60mins (adj) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check sensor for any faults/damage.\n2. Check sensor to controller cable/wire faults, loose connections.\n3. Verify voltage/current signals from sensor to controller terminals. Verify power supply to sensor.\n4. Check for any damage/faults in controller terminals.\n5. Validate the sensor point characteristics in controller software.\n6. Check manual overrides on front end/controller.");
s("name","oncoilsenOutofRange");
s("help2","On Coil Supply temperature sensor is higher than 140°F (adj) or lower than 41°F (adj) when equipment status is On.  The above conditions to remain true for >30mins (adj) 2 (adj) times or more in a day or >60mins (adj) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check sensor for any faults/damage.\n2. Check sensor to controller cable/wire faults, loose connections.\n3. Verify voltage/current signals from sensor to controller terminals. Verify power supply to sensor.\n4. Check for any damage/faults in controller terminals.\n5. Validate the sensor point characteristics in controller software.\n6. Check manual overrides on front end/controller.");
