s("help","Common/Header Condenser water Entering Temperature is more than SP (or Default SP of 25deg C) by 2 deg C when Chiller is On.\nThe above conditions were true for >30mins (adj) 2 (adj) times or more in a day or >60mins (adj) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Verify Cooling tower system is enabled and cooling tower fans are running as per the sequence.\n2. Check for manual overrides in Cooling tower system.\n3. Check CW common/header supply temp sensor location.\n4. Validate and verify the heat rejection system design.");
