s("help","VAV zone temp is more than setpoint by 5°C (adj.) and Reheat valve is close i.e.<5% or all Reheat stages are Off and AHU Status is On in occupied mode.\nAssociated AHU discharge temperature is satisfied.\nThe above conditions were true for >60mins (adj.) (2 times or more in a day) or >120mins (adj.) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1.Check if AHU DA temperature setpoint is set to higher value.\n2.Check Reheat valve AO Characteristics\n3.Check sensor location or any external influence Infiltration/Exfiltration)\n4.Check if Flow SP is as per design\n5. Check if Reheat Valve/Stage Relay is Stuck Open physically for VAV with Reheat\n6. Check Actuator Voltage/Power");
