s("dis","AHU Air Flow Sensor value out of limit");
s("ruleOn","air and flow and sensor and kind==\"Number\" and equipRef->ahu");
s("param","(_,_,/*loLimit:*/10,/*hiLimit:*/10000,/*minTime:*/60min,/*maxTime:*/120min,/*statuscheck:*/true,/*ruleWorkOrder:*/\"None\",/*freq:*/2,/*priority:*/\"Medium\",/*type:*/\"Operations\")");
s("param2","(_,_,/*loLimit:*/10,/*hiLimit:*/30000,/*minTime:*/60min,/*maxTime:*/120min,/*statuscheck:*/true,/*ruleWorkOrder:*/\"None\",/*freq:*/2,/*priority:*/\"Medium\",/*type:*/\"Operations\")");
s("help","AHU Airflow sensor is higher than 10000 L/sec (adj) or lower than 10 L/sec (adj) when AHU status is ON.\n\nThe above conditions to remain true for >60mins (adj) 2 (adj) times or more in a day or >120mins (adj) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\n  Recommendations:\n  1. Check sensor for any faults/damage.\n  2. Check sensor to controller cable/wire faults, loose connections.\n  3. Verify voltage/current signals from sensor to controller terminals.\n     Verify power supply to sensor.\n  4. Check for any damage/faults in controller terminals.\n  5. Validate the sensor point characteristics in controller\n     software.\n  6. Check manual overrides on front end/controller.\n");
s("name","ahuAirFlwSenOutOfRange");
s("help2","AHU Airflow sensor is higher than 30000 CFM (adj) or lower than 10 CFM (adj) when AHU status is ON.\n\nThe above conditions to remain true for >60mins (adj) 2 (adj) times or more in a day or >120mins (adj) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\n  Recommendations:\n  1. Check sensor for any faults/damage.\n  2. Check sensor to controller cable/wire faults, loose connections.\n  3. Verify voltage/current signals from sensor to controller terminals. Verify power supply to sensor.\n  4. Check for any damage/faults in controller terminals.\n  5. Validate the sensor point characteristics in controller software.\n  6. Check manual overrides on front end/controller.\n");
