s("param","(_,_,/*spdeviation:*/20,/*minTime:*/60min,/*threshold:*/5,/*maxTime:*/120min,/*freq:*/2,/*ahuPressureVal:*/50,/*znTmpLowLimit:*/10,/*znTmpHighLimit:*/35,/*flowLowLimit:*/10,/*flowHighLimit:*/1500,/*ahuVfdspeed:*/85,/*pressureSpdeviation:*/50,/*ahuvfdspeed:*/20,/*znTmpspLowLimit:*/18,/*znTmpspHighLimit:*/28,/*ruleWorkOrder:*/\"None\",/*priority:*/\"Low\",/*type:*/\"Comfort\")");
s("param2","(_,_,/*spdeviation:*/20,/*minTime:*/60min,/*threshold:*/5,/*maxTime:*/120min,/*freq:*/2,/*ahuPressureVal:*/0.2,/*znTmpLowLimit:*/50,/*znTmpHighLimit:*/95,/*flowLowLimit:*/10,/*flowHighLimit:*/3000,/*ahuVfdspeed:*/85,/*pressureSpdeviation:*/0.2,/*ahuvfdspeed:*/20,/*znTmpspLowLimit:*/64,/*znTmpspHighLimit:*/82,/*ruleWorkOrder:*/\"None\",/*priority:*/\"Low\",/*type:*/\"Comfort\")");
s("help","Box flow is lower than setpoint by 20% (adj.) or more and Difference between Zone temp and setpoint is more than 5°C (adj.) in occupied mode.\nAssociated AHU duct static pressure is satisfied.\nThe above conditions were true for >60mins (2 times or more in a day) OR >120mins once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check the Flow sensor and its tubing. If faulty, replace/calibrate as required.\n2. Check Damper & Actuator is properly coupled.\n3. Check if Damper is Stuck manually or overridden at Front end\n4. Check Controller output to actuator\n5. Check for leakage in duct before the VAV Box");
s("name","vavFlowLow");
s("help2","Box flow is lower than setpoint by 20% (adj.) or more and Difference between Zone temp and setpoint is more than 5°F (adj.) in occupied mode. Associated AHU duct static pressure is satisfied. The above conditions were true for >60mins (2 times or more in a day) OR >120mins once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check the Flow sensor and its tubing. If faulty, replace/calibrate as required.\n2. Check Damper & Actuator is properly coupled.\n3. Check if Damper is Stuck manually or overridden at Front end\n4. Check Controller output to actuator 5. Check for leakage in duct before the VAV Box");
