s("dis","Cooling Tower low effectiveness");
s("ruleOn","equip and coolingTower");
s("param","(_,_,/*threshold:*/60,/*minTime:*/30min,/*maxTime:*/60min,/*supplytempMinVal:*/5,/*supplytempMaxVal:*/40,/*returntempMinVal:*/5,/*returntempMaxVal:*/40,/*freq:*/2,/*ruleWorkOrder:*/\"None\",/*priority:*/\"Medium\",/*type:*/\"Energy\")");
s("param2","(_,_,/*threshold:*/60,/*minTime:*/30min,/*maxTime:*/60min,/*supplytempMinVal:*/41,/*supplytempMaxVal:*/104,/*returntempMinVal:*/41,/*returntempMaxVal:*/104,/*freq:*/2,/*ruleWorkOrder:*/\"None\",/*priority:*/\"Medium\",/*type:*/\"Energy\")");
s("help","Cooling tower effectiveness is less than 60% (adj) which indicates low cooling tower efficiency when cooling tower status is On.\n\nThe above conditions to remain true for >30mins (adj) 2 (adj) times or more in a day or >60mins (adj) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check if design water flow is maintained.\n2. Scaling in Cooling tower fills can cause reduced heat exchange.\n3. Check any hot air intake source near the tower.\n4. Check for irregular or lack of airflow in the tower.\n5. Check for blocked nozzles/sprays.");
s("name","cTLowEffectiveness");
s("help2","Cooling tower effectiveness is less than 20% (adj) which indicates low cooling tower efficiency when cooling tower status is On.\n\nThe above conditions to remain true for >30mins (adj) 2 (adj) times or more in a day or >60mins (adj) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check if design water flow is maintained.\n2. Scaling in Cooling tower fills can cause reduced heat exchange.\n3. Check any hot air intake source near the tower.\n4. Check for irregular or lack of airflow in the tower.\n5. Check for blocked nozzles/sprays.");
