s("dis","DA High Duct Static Pressure with Fan Speed < 85%");
s("help","AHU discharge duct static pressure is higher than setpoint by 20% (adj.) of setpoint and discharge fan speed is lower than 85% (adj.) when AHU status is On.\nThe above conditions to remain true for >30mins (adj.) 2 (adj.) times or more in a day or >60mins (adj.) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check if AHU discharge fan speed command is overridden between minimum speed and 85% on front end.\n2. Check for any mechanical issues/faults in discharge fan motor/VSD.\n3. Validate AHU discharge fan speed control logic in controller to ensure fan speed is commanded to minimum speed.\n4. Verify fan speed control design, discharge duct pressure setpoint, discharge duct pressure sensor location.");
