s("help","There is a mismatch between Isolation valve command and status.\nThe above conditions were true for >30mins (2  times or more in a day) OR >60mins once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check if valve is physically stuck at some position/manually overridden at field.\n2. Check for valve actuator faults and verify its operation, power supply, wire terminations.\n3. Check for any blockages in valve stem movement.\n4. Check for faults, loose connections in command and status cables and controller terminals.");
