s("help","Zone CO is higher than setpoint by 10% (adj) of CO setpoint and Fan is off.\nThe above conditions to remain true for >30mins (adj) 2 (adj) times or more in a day or >60mins (adj) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check if fan command is manually overridden on front end or fan local panel.\n2. Check fan status sensor for any faults.\n3. Check and verify the voltage signals from controller to fan command relay.\n4. Check for any faults in fan command relay or fan local panel. Check for any fan mechanical faults.\n5. Validate CO control logic in controller.");
