s("ruleOn","equip and fan");
s("help","There is a mismatch between Equip run status and run command. Command is \"ON\" while status is \"OFF\".\n\nLogic:\n1. This fault will trigger if Equip run command is \"ON\" and status is \"OFF\" for minimum time period of 30min adj.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Make sure Equip status point is not in “MAN” mode and forced to “Off” state\n2. Check if Equip is in \"Alarm\"\n3. Verify if the Equip run status sensor is faulty, calibrate or replace it if required");
s("name","equipFailtoStart");
s(o,"There is a mismatch between Equip run status and run command. Command is \"ON\" while status is \"OFF\"");
