s("help","Difference between AHU entering hot water temperature and leaving hot water temperature is less than 5degC (adj) [HWST - HWRT < 5degC] when AHU is running.\nThe above conditions to remain true for >30mins (adj) 2 (adj) times or more in a day or >60mins (adj) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check plant/common hot water supply temp is maintained at setpoint as per design.\n2. Check for any closed manual valves in AHU hot water line or any blockages to hot water flow.\n3. Verify hot water supply temp & return temp sensor location.\n4. Verify AHU hot water valve operation.\n5. Verify design flow and pressure is maintained across AHU hot water coil.");
