s(o,"Return a debug grid from the rule engine.  The mode string\ndetermines what information is queried:\n  - 'summary': configuration and KPIs for rule engine\n  - 'rules': summary of configured rules and their status\n  - 'rule (ruleId)': targets and status for a specific rule\n  - 'rules': summary of configured targets and their status\n  - 'target (targetId)': rules and status for a specific target\n  - 'targetRule (targetId, ruleId)': matrix of dates for given target/rule\n\nNote: the grid format of each mode response maps to what is shown in the\nRule|Debug screen.  However, the grid format is subject to change.\n\nExamples:\n   ruleDebug(\"summary\")\n   ruleDebug(\"rules\")\n   ruleDebug(\"rules\", @ruleId)\n   ruleDebug(\"targets\")\n   ruleDebug(\"target\", read(ahu))\n   ruleDebug(\"targetRule\", read(ahu), read(rule and ruleOn==\"ahu\"))\n");
