s("help","Zone/Building/Site PM2.5 sensor is higher than 35 ug/m3 (adj).\nThe above conditions to remain true for >30mins (adj) 2 (adj) times or more in a day or >60mins (adj) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1.This areas particulate reading is out of Healthy Building Wellness Guidelines.\n2.Verify no work is being done in the area.\n3.Verify outdoor air dampers are set correctly. 4.Verify filtration is clean.\n5.Verify no external source of air is infiltrating area.\n6.Verify ozone generator is working correctly, if equipped.\n7.Replace sensor.");
