s(o,"Do a \"parameter sweep\" by invoking the given func for all combinations\nof parameters in the parameter grid.\n\n- func: The function to invoke. You may also pass the Str name of\n  any function in this extension.\n- paramGrid (Dict or Dict[]): They keys of each Dict are the parameter\n  names of the func. The value of each key may be a single value, or\n  a list of values. Every combination of the value will be used to invoke\n  the given func\n\nReturns a list containing the result of invoking the function for\neach parameter combination.\n\nExamples:\npre>\n  // Get 5 instances of a configured RBF kernel\n  mlParamSweep(mlRbfKernel, [{\"gamma\": [null, 0.1, 0.2, 0.5, 1.0]}])\n<pre\n");
