s("help","Air pressure sensor is higher than 600 Pa (adj) or lower than 1 Pa (adj) when equipment status is On.\n\nThe above conditions to remain true for >30mins (adj) 2 (adj) times or more in a day or >60mins (adj) once in a day to trigger the fault.\n\nRecommendations:\n1. Check sensor for any faults/damage.\n2. Check sensor to controller cable/wire faults, loose connections.\n3. Verify voltage/current signals from sensor to controller terminals. Verify power supply to sensor.\n4. Check for any damage/faults in controller terminals.\n5. Validate the sensor point characteristics in controller software.\n6. Check manual overrides on front end/controller.");
