s("help","Identify if the average energy consumption of a specific day(weekday/weekend) is greater than the last month's average energy consumption (weekday/weekend) by the deviation specified.\n\nLogic:\n1. Check if the calculated energy consumption of the day is for a weekday or a weekend AND\n2. Compare the weekday value with the last month's weekday average OR compare the weekend value with the last month's weekend average.\n3. Identify if the difference is more than 30%.adj\n\nRecommendation:\n1. Check if the meter generating the spark is reading the correct values.\n2. Check if the systems that are monitored by the meter are running in manual.If yes, put them back in auto.");
